Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.46,0:00:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,但是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.34,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喉咙好干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,要水的话  我没带来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.09,0:00:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你其实有带来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.37,0:00:23.27,Comment,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我也匆匆忙忙就过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.94,0:00:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,已经不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.45,0:00:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.87,0:00:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,这样下去的话  我们在回去的路上会出现脱水症状
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  你有在这座岛上发现些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.94,0:00:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,发现什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.86,0:00:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,话说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.84,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  你说不小心闯进的洞穴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,脚底下都黏黏的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.25,0:01:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有股臭味
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,做…做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是蝙蝠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.32,0:02:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,有看到它们从岛离开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.94,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这里就是巢穴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.20,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.40,0:02:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,这座岛上没有蝙蝠的饵食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.77,0:02:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是雨水聚集而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,是淡水
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.92,0:02:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.45,0:02:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你闻闻看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.73,0:02:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是污水?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.33,0:02:37.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看来是被蝙蝠的粪便污染了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.86,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,直接喝的话  可能会出现什么感染病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.47,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是说  没办法取得水分吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.19,0:02:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.14,0:02:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪我  把誉也拖下水了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.64,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.84,0:02:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  你立了大功
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然这水不干净
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.09,0:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这样还是有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.29,0:03:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,无需在这里久留
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,来  虽然有些严峻  马上准备一下就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,先收集漂流物  重组一个竹筏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.89,0:03:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.31,0:03:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,誉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.35,0:03:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,这个怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.25,0:03:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,装在竹筏的后面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:44.87,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs45\fsp5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H12EFFF&\3c&H2C5652&\b1\pos(267,488)\frz7.893}笨蛋无视岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:44.87,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\fn萝莉体-DDC.yolan\fs45\fsp5\bord4.5\shad0\c&H2EFDC1&\3c&H2C5652&\b1\frz354.9\pos(1019,160)}蝙蝠岛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.54,0:03:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音是顺着海流漂到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.12,0:03:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去的话正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说让宝特瓶飘向正后方前进就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.73,0:03:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然可能靠不太住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,先把想到的先做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,要回去岛上了  紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.56,0:03:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.52,0:04:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,才刚说完
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,头…头好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.76,0:04:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,晕晕的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,水  我要喝水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.52,0:04:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.38,0:04:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我也差不多快要出现脱水症状了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.31,0:04:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我说  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.18,0:04:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才那洞穴的污水  要用在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.26,0:04:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,姑且我想尝试用紫外线消毒的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.91,0:04:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,消毒?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.19,0:04:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.04,0:04:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,看来不太顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,假设就算还没消完毒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.55,0:04:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得也…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.20,0:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.74,0:04:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道如果喝下去会怎样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.14,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.80,0:04:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,具体来说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.07,0:05:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,会在30分钟内出现腹泻和呕吐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这会比喝下去的水还要失去更多
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.41,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,很快我们就会陷入行动困难
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,岛也回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  我们也必须马上补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.97,0:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  那水不能喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.73,0:05:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那么该怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.68,0:05:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.93,0:05:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,其实大肠也能吸收水分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.87,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.67,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,用肛门喝这个水
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就不会经过胃  安全性很高!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,肛门?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,把屁股面对我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.17,0:05:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,脱下内裤  紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不要  不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.23,0:05:50.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.01,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,当…当然  不想死啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是  没…没办法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,要我露出那地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,再说要怎么…进不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.28,Default,,0,0,0,,进得去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.65,0:06:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我用嘴灌进去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你尽管放松  仰望天空的云朵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.02,0:06:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我  好像失去了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不对
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.62,0:06:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是为了生存
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,没错  一定是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.91,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  我知道你现在还很难受
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但还有一项工作要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.61,0:06:46.33,Comment,,0,0,0,,这是逼不得已  不算数
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.52,0:06:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,总之先注入十口分量的水
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那样就大概有200毫升
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我也差不多不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:06:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.19,0:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,就像把舌头塞进去那样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.32,0:07:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.02,0:07:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不要  饶了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.69,0:07:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是为了活下去  紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,誉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:21.56,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的事  只有天知地知你知我知
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.13,0:07:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,喂  紫音!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.43,0:07:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了  叫那么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.34,0:07:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,睦  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,誉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.31,0:08:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是明日香和睦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音  你这次真的很努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.77,0:08:17.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们马上就能上岸了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.34,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.21,0:08:27.30,Default,,0,0,0,,大家!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.74,0:08:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来  紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.47,0:08:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了  真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.74,0:08:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,天真会致命
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要将自己的性命放第一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸  对不起没有遵循你的教导
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.63,0:08:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.06,0:08:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都担心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.25,0:08:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.59,0:08:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是安全回来真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.09,0:09:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,誉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在过去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.49,0:09:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样  很丰盛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.79,0:09:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我和睦两个人一起准备的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.85,0:09:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然做不了黄油烤龙利鱼  但我们做成嫩煎了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很丰盛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.13,0:09:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.86,0:09:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们快点开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.81,0:09:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.32,0:09:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,非常好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃点  紫音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,你也吃吧  誉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.50,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.86,0:09:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,话说回来  你都忘记带水了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.25,0:09:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们没事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.27,0:09:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那个  用肛…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.65,0:09:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,毅力  用毅力!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.28,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,只要有毅力就无所不能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.64,0:09:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,誉  明天要做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.21,0:10:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是该去看看陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.92,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们再去找甜食吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.04,0:10:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,是…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.49,0:10:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,睡着了?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.77,0:10:16.01,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.23,0:10:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,今天要去设置抓野猪的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.70,0:10:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,在这之前  把这个抹在手上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.08,0:10:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,野猪屎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.37,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.63,0:10:44.22,Default,,0,0,0,,真…真的要抹这个?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.34,0:10:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,能用泥巴代替吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,野猪的鼻子很灵敏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.82,0:10:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦闻到人类的味道  就不愿意接近陷阱了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.94,0:10:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,别那么多废话  快抹!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.96,0:11:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不行  绝对不行  绝对不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.50,0:11:02.68,Comment,,0,0,0,,黏糊糊的  非常黏!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:05.07,Comment,,0,0,0,,好臭!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.74,0:11:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,紫音也快点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,誉  饶了她吧
